Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.94,0:00:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Always keep your poker face...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.26,0:00:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking my father's teaching to heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.04,0:00:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The miracle magician glides amidst the skycraper.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.35,0:00:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I come, Kid the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.55,0:00:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's target is the Red Tear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.29,0:00:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it's showtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.90,0:02:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The Secret of the Red Tear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.97,0:02:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief again declares war!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,To go after the world's biggest ruby,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.38,0:02:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,owned by the Hopper Magician's Troupe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.18,0:02:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph, he fails at every attempt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.15,0:02:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But he just never gives up, that little thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh…there are reasons I didn't steal those jewels
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps he should give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.16,0:02:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up what, Akako?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking to Kid the Phantom Thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.40,0:02:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That little…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.90,0:02:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That ruby has a history.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.77,0:02:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's known as the devil's stone,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.67,0:02:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and it brings misfortune to anyone who tries to take it…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.54,0:02:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The Red Tear…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.48,0:02:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hakuba…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.51,0:02:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if The Kid insists, then I suppose he insists…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.78,0:02:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, I have no interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.62,0:03:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Spider's in the middle of touring Europe…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.89,0:03:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't come after The Kid…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.43,0:03:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.76,0:03:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a pretty girl is in this class?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're blushing, Hakuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.14,0:03:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.04,0:03:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Red Tear…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.21,0:03:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, that jewel,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A long time ago…my father…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Nakamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.99,0:03:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a warning notice from Kid the Phantom Thief…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Dear Inspector Nakamori, I'm sorry but I cancelled my announcement."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, a cancellation notice…!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.20,0:03:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaaaat!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.50,0:03:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,"Kid the Phantom Thief"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He's cancelling!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"Kid the Phantom Thief Announcement Cancellation!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.94,0:03:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The police department has stated that last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.41,0:03:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief sent a cancellation notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:04:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps he will declare that he is retiring soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.22,0:04:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Making things up…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.15,0:04:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.66,0:04:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They've been showing this news over and over since this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.69,0:04:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He must feel threatened by my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.96,0:04:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What a wimp!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I ever be scared of that dumb Inspector…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.93,0:04:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The Leader of the Hopper Magician's Troupe, who owns the ruby,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Jody Hopper stated that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.08,0:04:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,she is disappointed that he won't be able to see him do his magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.88,0:04:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.45,0:04:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He just stole Aoko's wallet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.02,0:04:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you…!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on, Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.57,0:04:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your wallet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! When did I drop it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.61,0:04:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:05:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She stole it back in an instant…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.01,0:05:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.75,0:05:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.02,0:05:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the Japanese let pacifism lull them into a\Nsense of false security.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.53,0:05:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,…Oh! Are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you from the Hopper Magician's Troupe!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.10,0:05:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the Leader of the Troupe, Jody Hopper…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.70,0:05:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So she's a magician. That explains it…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.44,0:05:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been in the papers and on TV all morning…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.28,0:05:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Her grandfather was "The Flame Conjurer,"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.28,0:05:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,James Hopper, one of the major magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.95,0:05:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, um, Kaito's father was also a magician named Toichi Kuroba.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my! …I know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Toichi Kuroba, the greatest hands in the business…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.03,0:05:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,he's no different than my grandfather, or even that pickpocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:05:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.94,0:06:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Profiting from deception.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.97,0:06:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all just swindlers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.81,0:06:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's something wrong with those who get deceived too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,B, but don't you do magic, too…?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I took over from my grandfather when he\Npassed away two years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.86,0:06:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,because I didn't have a choice…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But, tonight will be my last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Last?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.00,0:06:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight is the Hopper Magician's Troup's last show.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.37,0:06:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of you should come if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.50,0:06:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.07,0:06:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to be deceived by a group of swindlers like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the organization!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.35,0:06:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They're after the Red Tear after all…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.69,0:06:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But... That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:06:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaito, we're going to be late for the movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.13,0:07:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,These are tickets for a dinner show in Minato Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.10,0:07:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going of course, right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.50,0:07:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph, no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not watching their show, when they look down on magicians!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.21,0:07:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Kaito,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.71,0:07:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to be that stubborn
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.15,0:07:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not being stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.92,0:07:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't hurry, we'll be late to the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,…Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.79,0:07:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There's even a restaurant with a view on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And the dinner show's on the fifth floor…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.33,0:07:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please refrain from any reckless behavior, young master!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.74,0:07:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.97,0:07:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's…who's reckless now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.75,0:07:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,…Right about now,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.22,0:07:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that persistent Inspector Nakamori
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.35,0:07:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,got his detectives standing by…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:08:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And that organization's all ready, having dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.50,0:08:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Kid the Phantom Thief, really not coming!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That little scoundrel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.41,0:08:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaito…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.74,0:08:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He should have come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so stubborn…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.05,0:08:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is on schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Implement the plan at the appointed time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.13,0:08:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, father?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.13,0:08:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you making that face.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.13,0:08:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kid's not coming, just enjoy yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.70,0:08:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.90,0:08:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful, wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.04,0:08:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,…And Aoko's probably in a bad mood
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave it to you, Jii
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.29,0:09:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Be safe, sir…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not right…like this…and…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.43,0:09:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this…and…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Like that…and…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to do that move faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.34,0:09:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,…Huh…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.67,0:09:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Swifter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Like that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,…Who are you…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.58,0:09:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're practicing hard, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.45,0:09:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my last chance to show the Leader that I have skills…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I want her to reconsider, and keep this magician group going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, can you do it one more time…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.30,0:09:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Please. Will you show that move one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.70,0:09:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I have a favor to ask you instead
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.38,0:10:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That person over there,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Leader of the Troupe, Jody!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.45,0:10:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh… Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,In her chest...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.99,0:10:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be the biggest ruby in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.56,0:10:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a ruby, but it shines blue…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.06,0:10:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How beautiful…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you a member of the troupe?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Y, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Does she always wear that ruby?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.97,0:10:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.51,0:10:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost our troupe's trademark.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.21,0:10:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been passed down from the first Troupe Leader, James,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Troupe Leader always wears it during our shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.42,0:10:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Jody's appearance isn't in the program…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.13,0:10:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That is because…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.99,0:10:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Since losing her parents in an accident ten years ago…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.93,0:10:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,…An accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:10:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.54,0:11:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,In the middle of a show.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.67,0:11:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the day,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.67,0:11:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,that they had inherited the ruby,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.34,0:11:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,as the new Troupe Leaders, as husband and wife…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.78,0:11:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be what Akako was talking about,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.79,0:11:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,when she said it was the devil's stone…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She has never done magic since.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.86,0:11:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe she resents magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.23,0:11:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the thing that took her parent's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.30,0:11:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,James regretted that, to his dying breath
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Jody…that's why…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.39,0:11:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There's another one
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.93,0:12:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,…Paul! That was great!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.10,0:12:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But, to think Paul is this good…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! At long last, we've come to the show's finale!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And for our final magical performance…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the finale to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.92,0:12:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.70,0:12:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let him get away!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.80,0:12:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,After him!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.34,0:12:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.01,0:12:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Troupe Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.72,0:12:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.82,0:13:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Paul, uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam, please, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.13,0:13:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax, I won't kill anyone yet
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll count to three.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.71,0:13:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to be hurt, give me the ruby
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.88,0:13:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam, that ruby…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.38,0:13:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Robert!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.15,0:13:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Two…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,…Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.59,0:13:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Paul!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What a fool…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.80,0:13:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait…Kid!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.38,0:14:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kid is shooting…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.30,0:14:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, young lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This cursed stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.34,0:14:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.61,0:14:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, madam…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.54,0:14:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot hand that over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.48,0:14:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Paul, are you…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.21,0:14:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.72,0:14:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wearing a bullet proof vest
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.49,0:14:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why were you…?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.89,0:14:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because…I am…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.83,0:14:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.23,0:14:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You son of a…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Kid was just…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.03,0:14:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He must have been a decoy sent by these men
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.97,0:15:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to lure the police away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.64,0:15:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You came for the ruby too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.81,0:15:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't come to steal it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.51,0:15:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.21,0:15:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,To protect you and the ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Paul?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I had him hide for awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.90,0:15:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You will see him soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,…So you were the one on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.54,0:15:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was too good for Paul.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.58,0:15:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.05,0:15:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I appeared after Paul performed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.89,0:15:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That was his magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And he wanted you to see it…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.70,0:16:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They've caught up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.71,0:16:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.55,0:16:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! You are James' Hopper's granddaughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.89,0:16:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.76,0:16:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That was wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you weren't going to do magic anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.77,0:16:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's thanks to the life long training
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I received from my grandfather and parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.87,0:16:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.84,0:16:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know about me…?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.84,0:16:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A petty thief who never learns.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.69,0:16:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you've done it, little girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.43,0:17:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you have to protect me and this ruby?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.57,0:17:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me, Kid!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"Revolving View Restaurant"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, please evacuate in a calm and orderly manner!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.98,0:17:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.88,0:17:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still flying around!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.32,0:17:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Mr. Snake!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.12,0:17:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He's stopped giving orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.39,0:17:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.42,0:17:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to time to play with you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.23,0:17:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.93,0:17:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been working really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But her ruby isn't the Pandora you're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.80,0:17:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more valuable than that…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.47,0:17:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that you'd understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.94,0:17:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be the judge of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.82,0:18:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.75,0:18:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I messed with the rotation apparatus a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.94,0:18:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell your boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.80,0:18:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll squash his organization if it's the last thing I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.51,0:18:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you're going to hurt me with that little toy…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.63,0:18:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Just in time for your friend to pick you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.74,0:18:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kid's fallen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:18:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Jii really was a little too reckless…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.82,0:19:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,…Thank you, Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.95,0:19:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We're safe…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.06,0:19:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But this really is "the devil's stone."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.86,0:19:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of it, the troupe members were hurt,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.46,0:19:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the show was ruined…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.73,0:19:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a cursed final show…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you ever think it was strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That ruby?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.41,0:19:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruby's are usually red, but that one's blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.48,0:19:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's called the Red Tear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.75,0:19:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Red…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.32,0:19:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The red of a flame…?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.15,0:19:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.36,0:19:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.09,0:19:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This was your grandfather, the fire conjurer,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,James Hopper's final magic trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.81,0:20:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandfather…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.41,0:20:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, Mother…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.48,0:20:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,To my dearest Jody.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.45,0:20:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember again for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The excitement you felt the first time you were onstage…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.96,0:20:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I pray that when this ruby shines red,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That the child of magic, Jody Hopper, will once again return to magic…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,…Grandfather
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.57,0:20:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.91,0:20:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, wow, that person's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.41,0:20:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He used the reflection angles of the ruby to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.95,0:20:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.88,0:20:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And the name of the ruby is the Red Tear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.75,0:20:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a special magic trick he put into the jewel for his granddaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.72,0:20:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I protected it, Dad…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.70,0:20:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd forgotten…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.23,0:21:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That I looked so happy doing magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.77,0:21:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandfather and my parents were all strict in their magic training.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.84,0:21:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But…they always watched over me with kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.35,0:21:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And they still do, even now…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.22,0:21:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Troupe Leader!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.99,0:21:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness you're safe…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.92,0:21:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Paul!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.79,0:21:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you stay on in this magician's troupe?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.87,0:21:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.33,0:21:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better keep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.57,0:21:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be on stage from now on too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.11,0:21:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Troupe Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.78,0:21:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.44,0:21:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.18,0:21:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.45,0:21:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.05,0:21:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't ever forget again…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.60,0:22:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.53,0:22:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiiiiiiid…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.04,0:22:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.58,0:22:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.78,0:22:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. So you did come, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.62,0:22:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I could do a show like this on my own, no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.55,0:22:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, do it! Right here right now!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.35,0:22:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Dummy. I'm done with tricks for the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.29,0:22:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,After the Red Tear, anything I did would pale in comparison.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.24,0:24:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.78,0:24:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief shows no sign of rest these long autumn nights!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.01,0:24:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The bad omen in Akako's crystal ball…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.32,0:24:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She says Kid the Phantom Thief's going to disappear!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.59,0:24:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that overly confident Hakuba,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.32,0:24:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A mysterious assassin, and even a fake Kid shows up…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.16,0:24:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph…even if it is a trap, I'm a Phantom Thief,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.03,0:24:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stop going after my prey!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.00,0:24:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on "Magic Kaito,"\N"The Witch, the Detective, and the Phantom Thief"!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.74,0:24:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you under the moonlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.91,0:24:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Next Kid's magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.21,0:24:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,"Broomstick"
